{"id": "1188537288716734594", "channel_id": "1188535084542861313", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048973279500701797", "author_name": "nesoteric", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然狂氣爆發上沒有說明，但是在死亡抵抗的描述中是有“觸發後在本次調查中幾率減半，獲得的死亡抵抗減半”的描述，所以說我們血肉就是這麽弱（", "timestamp": "2023-12-24T17:42:51.585000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188535084542861313", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」戰斗中血肉菲茵特狂氣爆發與其說明有所變化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
